        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C.) In nomine sancte+ et individue+ trinitatis. <persName ref="#people/7"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Otto</persName> div[ina favente clement]ia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Si aecclesiis dei devote
                        que+ famulantes eis petierint contulerimus, aeternae recompensationis
                        premium procul dubio accipere non ambigimus. Quapropter omnium sancte+ dei
                        aecclesiae fidelium nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum noverit
                        sagacitatis industria, quomodo nos interventu <persName key="#Bishops"><name
                                ref="Adalbertus">Adelberti</name></persName> nostri dilecti <rs
                            key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> per <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            >nostram preceptalem paginam</rs>
                        <rs key="#Allocation_to_churches">confirmavimus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs><orgName
                            key="#Allocation_to_churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1423"
                            > sancti Petri in Ce+lo aureo</orgName> cui <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/3960">Azo</persName> venerabilis <rs key="#Abbots"
                            >abbas</rs> preesse videtur, omnem <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terram</rs> quam in partibus Tuscie+ habere visum est, per diversos <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatus</rs> vel loca, scilicet in <geogName
                            ref="#estates/83" key="#Comitatus">comitatu Florentino</geogName><rs
                            key="#Curtes"> curtem </rs><geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#estates/4018"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4915">Campi</placeName></geogName> cum suis
                        pertinentiis, curtem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4019">Granianum</geogName> cum suis pertinentiis, prope
                        curtem Campi <rs key="#Churches">e+cclesiam </rs>unam cum suis pertinentiis,
                        in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Churches #Aldius #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4020"><placeName ref="#places/4906"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Linare</placeName></geogName> curtem cum aecclesia et suis
                        pertinentiis, in ipso Linare <rs key="#Aldius">aldiones</rs> decem, in
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4021"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4907">Olena</placeName></geogName> curtem unam cum
                        pertinentiis suis, infra <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/2"><geogName
                                key="#Houses #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Fruits/vegetables #Churches"
                                ref="#estates/4031">Florentiam</geogName></placeName> curtem unam
                        cum aecclesia et <rs key="#Houses">casa cum tribus caminatis et uno
                            solario</rs> et duobus <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">ortis</rs> et
                        omnibus aliis suis pertinentiis, in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4022"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4908">Ramiano</placeName></geogName> curtem unam cum
                        suis pertinentiis, in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4023"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4916">Gallinone</placeName></geogName> curticellam
                        unam, in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Manentes"
                            >Blaude</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Manentes">manentem</rs> unum, in <placeName ref="#places/506"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/4024">Fesule</geogName></placeName> curtem unam, in
                            <placeName ref="#places/4909"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/4025">Rontet</geogName></placeName> curtem unam, in
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4026"><placeName ref="#places/4910"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Cellule</placeName></geogName> curtem unam cum suis [pert]inentiis,
                        in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4027"><placeName ref="#places/4917"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Saniano</placeName></geogName> curtem unam, in <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/4918"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/4032">Casaentino</geogName></placeName> curtem unam,
                        in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4028"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4911">Maurana</placeName></geogName> curtem unam, in
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4029">Mediana</geogName> curtem unam cum pertinentiis
                        suis, in [... cur]tem unam, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4030">curtem <placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4912">Tartilese</placeName></geogName> cum suis
                        pertinentiis, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/4021">curtem <placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/4907">Olenam</placeName></geogName> prope <orgName
                            key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3579">plebem sancti
                            Uiti</orgName> sitam et quicquid in decimo Manisso[...]o, in fine
                            <placeName ref="#places/2">Florentie</placeName>+, in <placeName
                            ref="#places/4913">Uallia</placeName>, in <placeName ref="#places/4914"
                            >Sufficuano</placeName>, in Orbanula, prope montem sancti Martini et
                            iuxta<orgName key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3580">
                            plebem sanctae Mariae in <placeName ref="#places/4919"
                                key="#Baptismal_churches">Octinula</placeName></orgName> seu in
                            <placeName ref="#places/4911">Maurana</placeName> vel in aliis
                        quibuscumque locis predictum monasterium habere videtur, cum familiis
                        utriusque sexus et omnibus aliis rebus eidem monasterio pertinentibus, ea
                        videlicet ratione quatinus predictus abbas ac sui successores de omnibus
                        prescriptis rebus habeant potestatem possidendi ordinandi disponendi vel
                        quicquid eorum voluntas ad utilitatem prefati monasterii decreverit
                        faciendi, remota omnium hominum contradicione vel molestatione. Si quis
                        igitur hoc nostrum preceptum temere irrumpere temptaverit, sciat se
                        compositurum auri optimi libras centum, medietatem kamerae nostrae et
                        medietatem prelibati monasterii rectoribus. Quod ut verius credatur et ab
                        omnibus hominibus firmius dilegentiusque in posterum observetur, propria
                        manu roborantes sigillo nostro iussimus insigniri. Signum domni Ottonis
                        (MF.) invictissimi imperatoris augusti. <persName key="#Chancellor"
                            ref="#people/3962">Heribertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> vice <persName ref="#people/223"
                            key="#Bishops #Archchancellor">Petri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi. (SI. D.) Data XIII. kal. aug. anno
                        dominicae incarnationis DCCCCXCVI, indictione VIIII, anno vero tercii
                        Ottonis [regnantis XIII, imper]ii autem eius pr[im]o; actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/60">Marila</placeName>; feliciter amen.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
